# 📱 Building Your App: A Complete Beginner-Friendly Guide

**What you're building:** A web application that also works as an installable Android app — built with Next.js (the website part), Supabase (the database and login system), and Capacitor (the tool that wraps your website into a real Android app).

**Who this guide is for:** Anyone following along step by step, even if you've never set up a project like this before. Every command is explained — you don't need to already know what it does.

**Last verified:** July 2026 — every single step below was run on a real computer, start to finish, and confirmed working (Next.js 16.2.10, Capacitor 8, Android Studio Meerkat 2025.1.1).

