## Part 4: Install Your App's Dependencies

This one command installs everything else your app needs: database tools, form handling, animations, icons, and more.

```bash
npm install @supabase/supabase-js @supabase/ssr @tanstack/react-query react-hook-form @hookform/resolvers zod axios zustand date-fns motion clsx tailwind-merge class-variance-authority next-themes lucide-react react-icons
```

This might take a minute or two — that's normal.

