## Daily Workflow Cheat Sheet

Once everything's set up, here's your routine every time you sit down to work:

**Starting your day:**

```bash
git pull
npm install
npm run dev
```

**Testing your changes on Android:**

```bash
npm run build
npx cap sync
CAPACITOR_ANDROID_STUDIO_PATH=/path/to/your/studio.sh npx cap open android
```

Then click **▶ Run** in Android Studio.

**Saving your work:**

```bash
git add .
git commit -m "Describe what you changed"
git push
```

